description: Since the dawn of time, mischievous troublemakers have been warned of his wrath, scholars have searched for traces of his existence and evildoers have been tormented by the unstoppable force that goes by a single name: The Harvester. Vicki and Justin's undercover investigation of the Harvester leads them to the research lab of the infamous Dr. Parsons: a twisted genius on the verge of a dark invention that will endanger every soul on earth. Little do they realize, the Harvester has his own score to settle with the deadly doctor, as all factions finally come face-to-face. With epic forces locked on a collision course, no one will escape unscathed!
